---
import Layout from '../../layouts/LayoutFr.astro';
---

<Layout title="Open Source" description="Barrel est 100% open source sous licence Apache 2.0. Pour l'hebergement manage et le support, voir Barrel Platform.">
  <section class="py-32 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/20 rounded-2xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">100% Open Source</h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-ink/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Barrel et chaque bibliotheque qui le compose sont sous licence Apache 2.0.
        Telechargez, forkez, modifiez et deployez ou vous voulez, entierement gratuit.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl border border-line/30 p-8 mb-12">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Gratuit</p>
            <p class="text-ink/60 text-sm">Pour toujours</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Apache 2.0</p>
            <p class="text-ink/60 text-sm">Sans restrictions</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Auto-heberge</p>
            <p class="text-ink/60 text-sm">Votre infrastructure</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
        <a href="https://github.com/barrel-db/barrel" class="border border-line/50 hover:border-accent text-ink px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          Barrel sur GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="/docs" class="border border-line/50 hover:border-accent text-ink px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition">
          Documentation
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Managed Hosting -->
      <p class="text-ink/60 text-sm mb-16">
        Besoin d'hebergement manage ? <a href="/fr/contact" class="text-accent hover:underline">Contactez-nous</a> pour un devis.
      </p>

      <!-- Contact CTA -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-coral/20 to-line/20 rounded-xl border border-coral/30 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Des Questions ?</h2>
        <p class="text-ink/70 mb-6">
          Besoin d'aide pour demarrer, ou envie de discuter des options de support et d'hebergement manage ?
        </p>
        <a href="/fr/contact" class="inline-block bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition">
          Contactez-nous
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
